Verification:
  1. display_offset() delegates to grid.display_offset(), starts at 0
  2. history_size() delegates to grid.history_size(), starts at 0
  3. scroll_up(n) → Scroll::Delta(n) increases display_offset
  4. scroll_down(n) → Scroll::Delta(-n) decreases display_offset
  5. scroll_page_up() → Scroll::PageUp, display_offset > 0
  6. scroll_page_down() → Scroll::PageDown, reduces offset after page_up
  7. snap_to_bottom() → Scroll::Bottom, resets offset to 0
  8. scroll_up clamped: can't scroll past history_size
  9. extract_grid_cells uses Line(row - display_offset) for viewport rendering
  10. Scrolled viewport shows correct history content (L2 at row 0 when offset=2)
  11. Unscrolled viewport shows latest content (L4 at row 0)
  12. 11 new tests covering all scroll and viewport paths
